{"tid":660023,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗皮膚問題","createTime":"2018-05-10T10:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T09:52:38.000Z","uid":178184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"013fe282eb4de2e77f6dcffcba7d3118b68a6f64","tid":660023,"uid":178184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"皮膚真係好困擾既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上年六月開始屋企隻唐狗大脾甩毛 有時會自己用牙係到咪自己   之後上網搵左啲食療試下比佢 但都無咩用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到一個月前佢無啦啦起左勁多紅色一撻撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻帶佢去左睇獸醫 個獸醫淨係話皮膚敏感 比左啲抗敏感藥同抗生素仲有魚油 食個陣就好 就食完個陣都無再紅 打比獸醫診所問需唔需要再覆診 佢地回覆話唔紅就唔需要 咁食曬藥 佢皮膚都唔紅 啲毛仲開始生緊 咁就無再開藥食 淨係返診所到配魚油 到早兩日去左旅行一兩日我同媽咪都唔係屋企  屋企得細妹同爸爸 一返到黎佢啲皮膚又紅返一撻撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會好似人咁結焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時佢係到r r到我心都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家有無好既獸醫診所醫皮膚好架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  或者有無supplement介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/184129_59faf307fa9a2b6b078107afd94e5ea9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F184129_59faf307fa9a2b6b078107afd94e5ea9.png&h=600f79d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係去完旅行返黎咁既情況"},{"pid":"e5d60c1fde38675c8626613e938254c83f71754c","tid":660023,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"皮膚病 ，加上最近落雨 潮濕更加容易痕。<br />\n我隻狗最初都係食藥 止到痕，食食下完全唔work ，甩晒毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb2282e900f15330e160b67218d9ee6e671266b","tid":660023,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:45:22.000Z","